name: UAE NFT - Mars Colonization | Kaiwan Shaban

metadata.name: Sphere of Life
metadata.description:
Setting foot on The Red Planet is bound to happen.

When we as humans land on Mars, we will no longer be 'Earthlings',

our citizenship will be 'Martians'. Afterall, the dry, lifeless planet we see today may have once been as habitable as Earth billions of years ago.
